stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle

    Idle --> SolarCharging : T_coll > T_tank_btm + 7°C\nAND collectors filled
    Idle --> SpeculativeRefill : collectors drained\nAND T_outdoor > 5°C AND daytime
    Idle --> GreenhouseHeating : T_greenhouse < 10°C
    Idle --> ActiveDrain : T_outdoor < 2°C\nAND collectors filled
    Idle --> Emergency : T_greenhouse < 5°C\nAND tank insufficient

    SolarCharging --> Idle : T_coll < T_tank_btm + 3°C\n(after min run time)
    SolarCharging --> ActiveDrain : T_outdoor < 2°C
    SolarCharging --> OverheatDrain : T_tank_top > 85°C

    OverheatDrain --> CollectorsDrained : flow sensor = 0
    ActiveDrain --> CollectorsDrained : flow sensor = 0

    CollectorsDrained --> Idle : waiting
    CollectorsDrained --> SpeculativeRefill : T_outdoor > 5°C\nAND daytime\nAND retry cooldown elapsed

    SpeculativeRefill --> SolarCharging : T_coll > T_tank_btm + 7°C\n(after min run time)
    SpeculativeRefill --> CollectorsDrained : T_coll too low\n(after min run time)

    GreenhouseHeating --> Idle : T_greenhouse ≥ 12°C
    GreenhouseHeating --> Emergency : T_greenhouse < 5°C\nAND tank insufficient

    Emergency --> Idle : T_greenhouse ≥ 10°C

    note right of Idle
        All valves CLOSED, all actuators OFF
        V_air fail-safe: OPEN when relay OFF
        (collectors stay drained)
    end note

    note right of SolarCharging
        VI-btm OPEN, VO-coll OPEN, V_ret OPEN
        Pump ON, Fan OFF
        Min run time after refill before evaluating stop
    end note

    note right of GreenhouseHeating
        VI-top OPEN, VO-rad OPEN
        Pump ON, Fan ON
        Supply: tank top → reservoir (air sep) → pump → radiator
    end note

    note right of ActiveDrain
        VI-coll OPEN, VO-tank OPEN, V_air OPEN
        Pump ON until flow=0
        Trigger: freeze protection
    end note

    note right of OverheatDrain
        Same valves/sequence as ActiveDrain
        Trigger: tank fully charged (T_tank_top > 85°C)
        Resume when T_tank_top < 75°C
    end note

    note right of SpeculativeRefill
        Uses solar_charging valve states
        Cold water drops T_coll initially
        Wait min run time, then evaluate
        Retry cooldown if sun insufficient
    end note

    note right of Emergency
        All valves CLOSED
        Space heater ON (2kW)
        Jäspi element ON (optional)
    end note
